{"tid":2246939,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"未能談妥駐韓美軍費用分攤 美軍方將讓南韓工人休無薪假","createTime":"2020-10-17T12:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T13:12:05.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37c260d83d3483e825285590441eb18d47768cb3","tid":2246939,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"美國軍方已經告知南韓政府，由於對 2.85 萬駐韓美軍費用分攤問題無法達成協議，明年 4 月起將讓近 9000 名南韓工人放無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n先前的特別措施協議 (Special Measures Agreement) 於 2019 年末到期後，南韓雙方仍持續談判，但進展微小。美方讓受雇於美軍基地的南韓工人，由 4 月起休無薪假，之後美韓在 6 月份達成一項臨時協議，由韓方為其中約 4000 人提供經費。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐韓部隊 (USFK) 於 10 月 5 日發信給南韓勞工部，稱時經費將於 12 月 31 日到期，美方只能繼續為這些工作人員支付費用到明年 3 月。<br />\n<br />\n美方表示，由於未能簽署特別措施協議或相關的協議，此後仍將面對 2021 年餘下時間經費不足的問題，這使韓籍工作人員將休無薪假，開始時間不早於 4 月 1 日。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普此前表示，南韓必須支付更多費用，不然他考慮撤離駐韓美軍。本週南韓國防部長徐旭 (Suh Wook) 和美國國防部長 Mark Esper 舉行年度安全會議，特別措施協議也是主要重點。<br />\n<br />\n由於未能談出結果，兩國最後發布的聯合公報上，美方未承諾「維持美國國防軍的當前兵力以保衛韓國」，這是過去年度會後聲明中通常會有的表述<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4534216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4534216&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1hCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=d473bd31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4534216</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southkorea-usa-troops/u-s-military-says-south-korean-workers-may-be-laid-off-amid-row-over-costs-idUSKBN2710FU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-southkorea-usa-troops%2Fu-s-military-says-south-korean-workers-may-be-laid-off-amid-row-over-costs-idUSKBN2710FU&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1hCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=a03de5b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-southkorea-usa-troops%2Fu-s-military-says-south-korean-workers-may-be-laid-off-amid-row-over-costs-idUSKBN2710FU&h=6208a3ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southkorea-usa-troops/u-s-military-says-south-korean-workers-may-be-laid-off-amid-row-over-costs-idUSKBN2710FU</a>"},{"pid":"33b55222490ae6db75a07b9669b55793143cbfc3","tid":2246939,"uid":121076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"咁種意刁大大，改由老解駐軍囉"},{"pid":"0e7d8e2be99934f8abb89db85557f611f7269006","tid":2246939,"uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"韓美聯合聲明12年來首次刪除&ldquo;維持駐韓美軍&rdquo;的語句<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2246817/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2246817/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6f21b7d7fc1371cb185a4c7dbec934da9b42f735","tid":2246939,"uid":251732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"畀唔起錢嘅就請你靠自己對付北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79da793d61c87a621331d577546f625c66ec2256","tid":2246939,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思可唔可以幫我推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求連登仔女全力支持特朗普競選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2246891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2246891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a168281a89866a7daecdb0e6f423275baddf7f0","tid":2246939,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"香港唔介意畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72306d18b8cc5cfa8c78f19cecb5aa612bfaf3d4","tid":2246939,"uid":91771,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"列定駐港美軍嘅軍費都差唔多了<br />\n唔係明日大嶼一起，香港就無錢帶路了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a553460776e5dfa3c853bec397a1e68bd84d367","tid":2246939,"uid":82359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"好似對德國咁直接搬去北韓<img